{
  "texts": [
    "Results for the non-TCGA datasets can also be found on our Github website https://github.com/jianglindong93/AUTOSurv.",
    "Following the procedures mentioned in 26, the SHAP values (contribution scores in our setting) of each LFSurv input feature were calculated for 100 randomly sampled high-risk-group patients.",
    "We present in Fig. 5 the SHAP value summary plots.",
    "Features on the Y-axis are sorted in descending order based on their overall contribution scores (averaged absolute SHAP values, see the \"Methods\" section).",
    "Within each row, each dot represents a patient, the color of the dot indicates its feature value, with red and blue corresponding to high and low values on the spectrum, respectively."
  ]
}